name: Always Adrift LONG SLEEVE
description:
Souths Landing Co. Always Adrift non pocket LS

A portion of ALL sales, and boxes of each shirt, will be given to support missionary work in Uganda to help build schools, and water ways, to the outer lying areas! Please support in this charity raise to better the future lives of children in Uganda, and ALL shirts come with a "thank-you" card from a child in Uganda!

PLEASE NOTE: These will be a PRE-ORDER shirt! I'm aiming to have 60 shirt orders to make them, and these will only be available for 2 weeks. If the 60 shirt order quote is not made, everyone will be refunded of their money through PayPal. So that means to buy one for the whole family :)
